---
title: Express Lemon & Sweet Chilli Pork with Ginger-Lemongrass Veggie Fried Rice & Coriander
description: Sweet, hot and tangy, these tender pork strips have it all! This fried rice has a mix of tender veg tossed through, and is flavoured with soy and fragrant ginger paste. Topped off with our supercharged, flavour-packed pork strips, this dish is sure to please!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
